&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Abacus Insights is transforming how data works for health plans. Our mission is simple: make healthcare data usable, so the people responsible for care and cost decisions can act faster, with confidence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
