&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This is an exciting opportunity for a data modeler with experience in Databricks, Snowflake, schema evolution, and modern data engineering practices to shape the future of healthcare data platforms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
